# Running Tests

pytest is not installed. Run test files directly:

```bash
# ❌ BAD
uv run python -m pytest dagnabbit/dag/tests/
python -m pytest ...

# ✅ GOOD
uv run python dagnabbit/dag/tests/test_batching_equivalence.py
uv run python dagnabbit/dag/tests/test_signal_propagation.py
```
